Less-than-professional scripts and the like for fun things to do.

master-beater   Create a metronome program for ctronome, use feh to display
                an image slideshow that then uses icy-build to evaluate the
                slideshow images to display "flavor text"

icy-build       Check the current slideshow image; If it matches criteria,
                display a message overlay, with instructions or status
                information

Sessions.pm     Perl module for master-beater and friends
